28 #include "Mixture.h"
29 #include "TransferModel.h"
30 
31 namespace Mutation {
32  namespace Transfer {
33 
43 class OmegaCElec : public TransferModel
44 {
45 public:
46  OmegaCElec(Mutation::Mixture& mix)
47  : TransferModel(mix)
48  {
49  mp_wrk1 = new double [mix.nSpecies()];
50  mp_wrk2 = new double [mix.nSpecies()];
51  };
52 
53  ~OmegaCElec()
54  {
55  delete [] mp_wrk1;
56  delete [] mp_wrk2;
57  };
58 
59  double source()
60  {
61  mixture().speciesHOverRT(NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, mp_wrk1, NULL);
62  mixture().netProductionRates(mp_wrk2);
63 
64  double sum = 0.0;
65 
66  for(int i = 0 ; i < mixture().nSpecies(); ++i)
67  sum += mp_wrk1[i]*mp_wrk2[i]/mixture().speciesMw(i);
68 
69  return (sum*mixture().T()*RU);
70  }
71 
72 private:
73  double* mp_wrk1;
74  double* mp_wrk2;
75 };
76 
77 // Register the transfer model
78 Mutation::Utilities::Config::ObjectProvider<
79  OmegaCElec, TransferModel> omegaCElec("OmegaCElec");
